## 📝 Key Information Quick Reference

### Technology Stack
```
Frontend: Kotlin, Android Studio, Material Design
Backend: Firebase (Firestore, Authentication, FCM)
Database: Firebase Firestore
ML: Python-based (Player Skill Prediction, Matchmaking)
```

### System Requirements
```
Development: 8GB RAM (16GB recommended), Windows/Mac/Linux, JDK 11+
Testing: Android 8.0+, 4GB RAM minimum
Deployment: Android API 24+ (Android 7.0+)
```

### Key Features
```
✓ Tournament Management
✓ Player Registration
✓ Match Scheduling
✓ Live Updates
✓ Real-time Notifications
✓ Streaming Integration
✓ Analytics & Reports
✓ Payment Processing
✓ ML-based Matchmaking
✓ Fraud Detection
```

